However  the agribusiness company's palm-oil refining margins could remain weak in 2Q due to weak oleochemical and biodiesel demand  he cautions. Commodity prices  including that of vegetable oils have also come off last year's highs  although sugar could be a bright spot  with prices expected to remain strong amid ongoing shortages  the analyst adds.
